# `LocalizedLabels` Definition

Contains localized labels used in messenger apps

| Property | Type | Required | Description |
|----------|------|----------|-------------|
| key | `string` | No | Contains localized label key used in messenger homescreen and push notification. PushNotificationTitle and PushNotificationBody keys are required when notifications are enabled. |
| value | `string` | No | Contains localized label value used in messenger homescreen and push notification |
